</head>

<body>

	{% assign showCannon = true %}
	{% assign showMiddleBadge = false %}
	{% include header.html %}


	<main id="main-content" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
		<div class="mb-16 mt-16 sm:mb-24 sm:mt-24 sm:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
				<div class="relative px-12 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
					<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
						<div class="max-w-xl text-base  mx-auto">
							<div class="mx-auto mb-4 mt-4">
								<img alt="Logo of Coffee & Fun LLC featuring a stylized cup with a coffee bean pattern, representing the company's focus on creativity and innovation in software development."
									src="assets/images/supporthumans.png" width="180" height="180"
									decoding="async" data-nimg="future" loading="lazy"
									class="aspect-square mx-auto block" />
							</div>

						</div>

						<div class="max-w-xl text-base  mx-auto">
							<div class="card my-8 bg-base-100 shadow-md">
								<div class="card-body">
									<h1 class="card-title mb-4 text-2xl">Welcome to I Support Humans </h1>
								
									<p class="mb-2 text-lg text-black">
										As artificial intelligence becomes a bigger part of our daily lives, it’s more important than ever to recognize, celebrate, and support the people behind the work we value most. From art and writing to craftsmanship and innovation, human creativity holds a unique and irreplaceable quality that no algorithm can replicate.
									</p>
									<p class="mb-2 text-lg text-black">
										This space for everyone who values the human touch in creativity, work, and ideas. This is not about rejecting progress, but about ensuring that as technology grows, we don’t lose sight of the people behind the brilliance.
									</p>

									<p class="mb-2 text-lg text-black">
										By signing our pledge, you’re taking a stand for human effort and originality in a world where automation and AI often take center stage. You’re helping to build a future where humans remain at the heart of innovation, artistry, and meaningful work.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class=" mx-auto max-w-7xl text-base mt-12" id="signPetition">
							<div
								class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-8 sm:grid-cols-2 ">
								<div class="card my-8 bg-base-100 shadow-md">
									<div class="card-body">
										<h2 class="card-title mb-10 text-3xl"> Our Statement</h2>

										<p class="mb-2 mt-2 text-lg text-black">As signatories of this pledge, we commit to supporting and advocating for human-created work.		</p>
										<p class="mb-2 mt-2 text-lg text-black">
										<b>We believe in:</b>
										</p>
										<ol class="list-decimal">
											<li class="mb-2">
												Promoting original content created by real people.
											</li>
											<li class="mb-2">
												Recognizing and celebrating the creativity, skill, and effort that only humans can bring.
											</li>
											<li class="mb-2">
												Encouraging ethical practices in technology and AI development.
											</li>
										</ol>
										<p class="mb-2 mt-2 text-lg text-black">
											<b>We stand against:</b>
										</p>
								
										
									
										<li class="mb-2">
										Misrepresentation of AI-generated work as human.
										</li>
										<li class="mb-2">
										Over-reliance on automation in areas where human skills matter most.
										</li>
										<li class="mb-2">
										Disregard for the value of human artistry and effort.
										</li>
										<li class="mb-2">
										By signing this list, you join a movement dedicated to preserving the beauty and authenticity of human work.
										</li>
									


										
											
									</div>
								</div>



								<div class="card my-8 bg-base-100 shadow-md">
									<div class="card-body">
										<h2 class="card-title mb-10 text-3xl">The list</h2>
									<ol class="list-decimal">
										{% for human in list.humans %}
									  <li class="mb-2">
										<a class="link link-hover" href="{{human.link}}" title="
										{{ human.name }}
										{% if human.title and human.title != '' %} working as a {{ human.title }}{% endif %}
										{% if human.company and human.company != '' %}, @ {{ human.company }}{% endif %}">
										  {{ human.name }}
										  {% if human.title and human.title != '' %}, {{ human.title }}{% endif %}
										  {% if human.company and human.company != '' %}, @ {{ human.company }}{% endif %}
										</a>
									  </li>
									  
									{% endfor %}
								
									</ol>
									<div class="mb-2 mt-4">
										<button onclick="my_modal_3.showModal()" class="btn btn-block btn-wide btn-secondary " title="Add your name to this list">Add your name to this list
										</button>
									  </div>
						
								</div>
								</div>

							</div>
						</div>

						<div class=" mx-auto max-w-7xl text-base mt-12" id="code">
							<div class="card my-8 bg-base-100 shadow-md">
								<div class="card-body">
									<h2 class="card-title mb-10 text-3xl"> Add This Badge to Your Website</h2>


									<div class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-md p-4 relative text-left bg-black">
										<pre id="badgeCode" class="overflow-auto text-sm">
										  <code>
											&lt;a href="https://www.isupporthumans.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;
											  &lt;img src="http://www.isupporthumans.com/assets/images/supporthumans.png" 
												alt="I support humans over AI" style="width:150px;"/&gt;
											&lt;/a&gt;
										  </code>
										</pre>
										<button 
										  class="btn btn-sm btn-primary absolute top-4 right-4"
										  onclick="copyCode()">
										  Copy Code
										</button>
									  </div>
									  
									  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
										Paste this code into your website footer to show your support!
									  </p>

									</div>

							</div>

						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>


<dialog id="my_modal_3" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-box">
    <form method="dialog">
      <button class="btn btn-sm btn-circle btn-ghost absolute right-2 top-2">✕</button>
    </form>
   
    <div class="p-4">
		<iframe src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe_YEyU8DMulCiBq8UDV9h6UuCMkFOTcqb4aJa2CrakdT9aKQ/viewform?embedded=true" width="100%" height="824" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0">Loading…</iframe>
	</div>
  </div>
</dialog>


<script>
  function copyCode() {
    const code = document.getElementById('badgeCode').innerText.trim();
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {
      alert('Code copied to clipboard!');
    }).catch(() => {
      alert('Failed to copy code.');
    });
  }
</script>

	</main>


	{% include modals.liquid %}


	{% include  footer.html %}



</body>

</html>